Types of test
------------------------
There are two types of test for every energy/object.

First test for normal state of streaming of energy ie for distinguish of stability, ie you senses,mind,observation..so on observe something is making stable it or non stable
it. or it distinguish the state of stabilize/dis stabilize it. This type of testing for separating the state of energy at current moment. 

Second test for storage in mind this types of testing is not only for current state of energy testing but also it keep in storage for further action. When one time you eat mangoes banana, sweet..so on later you can say this is fine for me, how do you know? this is nothing but the testing in your storage.

Similar way tension/sad/pain/happiness/delight/get lost/..so on are the test of energy within us. When we have lack of energy we feel tense with little-little situation. When
we try to steal energy from some one's heart and after continuous supply of energy some one suddenly stop the supply of energy and you get heart is  nothing but the test of sudden stoppage of energy.

Similar way life have also test at different state/phase of life. The child have different test of life than the young and the young have another test of life than old age.
The scientist have different test of life. The poet have different. The farmer have different..so on.

